thread.title_full: McElhinneys Department Store reviewed by Rebel shopper

author: Rebel shopper
title: Rebel shopper
text:
I chose super cute shoes on line. They were delivered without a hitch. The shoes were too high in the heel for me so I returned them. No hassle there though personally I hate forking out for return Post.
Maybe if the heel height was in the info it might be useful.
Lovely website to use.
